    content="Traditional Indian restaurant serving food from north and south India with a fully licensed bar. We provide table service, takeout, catering and a lunch buffet.">
  <title>Prince of India | Traditional Indian Cuisine | Home</title>
  <%- include src/views/templateParts/head-meta.ejs %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include src/views/templateParts/nav-bar.ejs %>
  <%- include src/views/templateParts/header.ejs %>
  <main id="main">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h3>A Slice of <span class="txt-orange">India</span> in Burlington</h3>
      <p>Our restaurant offers residents of Burlington a fully immersive Indian dining experience.</p>
    </div>
    <section id="info">
      <div class="slide-row">
        <div class="slide-block slidable" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="infoLabelMenu" >
          <div class="image" style="background-image: url('<%- require('../../assets/img/indian-food.jpg') %>')"></div>
          <div class="text">
            <h4 id="infoLabelMenu">Traditional Taste</h4 id="infoLabelBar">
            <p>We have a menu consisting of carefully selected traditional dishes which originate from North and South
              India. We have a wide range of poultry, lamb, fish and vegetarian curries, and do not serve any pork or
              beef.</p>
            <p>The exotic dishes on our menu include a mix of secret family recipes, which have been passed through
              multiple generations, and homeland comforts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-block slidable" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="infoLabelBar">
          <div class="image" style="background-image: url('<%= require('../../assets/img/indian-bar.jpg') %>');"></div>
          <div class="text">
            <h4 id="infoLabelBar">Fully Licensed Bar</h4>
            <p>No true Indian restaurant is complete without a fully equipped bar to match. And we are no different.</p>
            <p>Our bar is fully licensed and is happy to provide you with a wide range of beers (on tap and bottled),
              wines, spirits, juices and mixers.</p>
            <p>We also serve traditional Indian drinks such as Lassi (an Indian milkshake) and chai (tea), as well as
              bar
              snacks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hero-image" hero>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-heading">
          <h3>Discover <span class="txt-red">Something</span> Here</h3>
          <p>Some text to go below what you will discover</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-heading">
      <h3>A Slice of <span class="txt-orange">India</span> in Burlington</h3>
      <p>Our restaurant offers residents of Burlington a fully immersive Indian dining experience.</p>
    </div>
    <section id="services">
      <div class="tile-row">

        <div class="img-tile" aria-describedby="buffetDesc" aria-labelledby="buffetLabel" tabindex="0" style="background-image: url('<%- require('../../assets/img/indian-buffet-service.jpg') %>');">
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Buffet</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="template">
            <div class="heading">
              <p id="buffetLabel">Buffet</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content" id="buffetDesc">
              <p>
                We offer a traditional Indian lunch buffet which is sure to satisfy your taste buds and appetite.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our daily lunch buffet costs just $12.99 per person and is unlimited. It features a generous selection
                of traditional curries and sides, as well as rice, dips and salad.
              </p>
              <p>
                For more information about our Indian lunch buffet please see our <a class="service-link" href="/offers"
                  title="Prince of India's special offers">special offers</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="img-tile" aria-describedby="takeoutDesc" aria-labelledby="takeoutLabel"
          tabindex="0" style="background-image: url('<%- require('../../assets/img/indian-takeout-service.jpg') %>');">
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Takeout</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="template">
            <div class="heading">
              <p id="takeoutLabel">Takeout</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content" id="takeoutDesc">
              <p>
                If you would to eat your food in the comfort of your own home, that's no problem! We provide a full
                traditional Indian takeout service covering the local Burlington area.
              </p>
              <p>
                You can choose to have your food delivered by one of our takeout providers -- <a class="service-link"
                  href="" title="Prince of India on " rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Skip The Dishes</a>, <a
                  class="service-link" href="" title="Prince of India on " rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Door
                  Dash</a> -- or collect it from our restaurant yourself -- we currently offer a <a class="service-link"
                  href="/offers" title="Prince of India discounts">discount on collections</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="img-tile" aria-describedby="cateringDesc" aria-labelledby="cateringLabel"
          tabindex="0" style="background-image: url('<%- require('../../assets/img/indian-catering-service.jpg') %>');">
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Catering</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="template" id="cateringDesc">
            <div class="heading">
              <p id="cateringLabel">Catering</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>
                We are able to provide a traditional Indian catering service for any of your special occasions.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our catering service will enable you to serve all your favorite Indian dishes to your guests, with the
                same high standard you would expect in our restaurant.
              </p>
              <p>
                If you would like to bring the traditional flavours of our Indian cuisine to your event please contact
                us using our <a href="/contact" title="Contact Prince of India" class="service-link">contact form</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="img-tile" aria-describedby="alacarteDesc" aria-labelledby="alacarteLabel"
          tabindex="0" style="background-image: url('<%- require('../../assets/img/indian-a-la-carte-service.jpeg') %>');">
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Dining</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="template" id="alacarteDesc">
            <div class="heading">
              <p id="alacarteLabel">Dining</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
              <p>
                Our traditional Indian restaurant serves a wide variety of freshly prepared and traditional North and
                South Indian dishes.
              </p>
              <p>
                All dishes have been carefully selected using a mix of secret family recipes and national favorites.
              </p>
              <p>
                We provide our guests with a truly traditional experience and cater to all allergies and we do not keep,
                or serve, any pork or beef on our premises.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <%- include src/views/templateParts/footer.ejs %>
</body>

</html>